Peste des petits ruminants, Algeria
-----------------------------------
Information received on (and dated) 19 Mar 2012 from Dr Ahmed Chawki Karim Boughalem, [Director of Veterinary Services, Ministry of Agriculture and Rural Development], Alger, Algeria

Report type: immediate notification
Start date: 25 Feb 2012
Date of 1st confirmation of the event: 25 Feb 2012
Report date: 19 Mar 2012
Date submitted to OIE: 19 Mar 2012
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 20 Mar 2011
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: Morbillivirus
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to the whole country

New outbreaks
Outbreak 1: Baba Ami, Berriane, Berriane, Ghardaia
Date of start of the outbreak: 25 Feb 2012
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: farm
